(62, 3, 'normal', 'ISL 2017-18: Blasters to take ATK while Kochi kicks the Indian football festival', 'Kochi ', 'kfcbannerbig.jpg', '', '', 'The new Dutch-born head-coach of Kerala Blasters has already made it clear that his team will be playing an attacking football, which may bring a complete shift from the defensive style endorsed by the team in previous editions.', 'Db Correspondent', '', '2017-11-16', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\"><span> </span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span>With expensive foreign signings,\r\nnew teams, extended season and the recognition of Asian Football Confederation, the fourth edition of Indian\r\nSuper League is all set to kickstart the\r\nfootball festival on Friday with a grant inauguration ceremony by Bollywood stars like Salman Khan and Katrina Kaif and a\r\nlong list of celebrities performing and attending\r\nat Jawaharlal Nehru Stadium, Kochi. The defending champions, ATK will take on\r\nKerala Blasters in the inaugural match that will start at 8.00 pm. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span>Earlier the teams were gone behind big guns and brought many expensive\r\nplayers from foreign shores which include the Bulgarian legend and former\r\nManchester United player Dimitar Berbatov\r\nby Kerala Blasters, the ex-Irish international Robbie Keane by ATK and the Venezuelan\r\nstriker </span><span>Nicolás\r\nLadislao Fedor Flores<span> (Miku) for Bengaluru FC. <o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span>With the addition\r\nof hugely popular Bengaluru FC and Tata\r\nbacked Jamshedpur FC, Indian Super League now have a total of ten teams playing\r\n95 matches for a time span of </span><span>four months till March. The final match of this fourth edition is scheduled\r\non 17 March at Vivekananda Yuba Bharati Krirangan, Kolkata. </span><span >The Asian Football Confederation’s recognition to the league prior\r\nto this edition is a big boost raising the status of ISL to that must abide by the regulations of AFC and FIFA. According\r\nto the new rules, teams had to include at least six Indian players in the\r\nplaying eleven which will also decrease the number foreign players in a single\r\ngame. The champions of ISL’s fourth edition will be also playing in the playoff\r\nmatches of AFC Cup.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span>The God’s Own Team<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span>Kerala Blasters was one the few teams in ISL to complete the foreign\r\nsignings early and left no room for confusion which gripped the team during all\r\nthe previous seasons of the league. A\r\ncomplete revamp in the administration caused swift decisions and popular\r\nsignings of a new coach and several foreign signings. The team also had a good\r\ntime in calling for talented Indian players during the transfer market as the\r\ncoach said they could capture 90% of players they wished for. The greatest of all\r\nsurprises was the signing of Bulgarian hitman and former Manchester United\r\nlegend, Dimitar Berbatov. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span>Rene Meulensteen and\r\nthe attacking philosophy of game<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span>The new Dutch-born\r\nhead-coach of Kerala Blasters has already made it clear that his team will be\r\nplaying an attacking football, which may bring a complete shift from the\r\ndefensive style endorsed by the team in previous editions. Historically,\r\nBlasters had opted for head coaches who had put their interest more into the\r\ndefence system of the team which helped them to concede very few number of\r\ngoals compared to other teams. But with Meulensteen taking charge the fans\r\ncould expect a different game plan altogether. The former aid of Sir Alex\r\nFerguson at Manchester United has raised the hopes of fans too much. </span><span >With at least four ex-Manchester United men in the team,\r\nincluding defender Wes Brown and goalkeeper Paul Rachubka,  the yellow army may reflect the traits of Red\r\nDevils, hopes fans.</span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span> </span></p>', '1'),
(63, 4, 'normal', 'Nobel Prize 2017: 6 awards, 12 new laureates and everything you need to know', '', 'csmNobel.medal1052x45101aef6d076b2.jpg', '', '', 'On December 10, the 12 new Nobel Laureates will be honoured in a grant event at Stockholm, Sweden, when they receive the medals and diplomas from King Carl XVI Gustaf of Sweden. Meanwhile the Nobel Peace Prize Laureates receive their award from the chairman of Norwegian Nobel Committee in a completely different event held at Oslo, Norway. \r\n\r\n', 'Db correspondent ', '', '2017-11-17', '<p><b>Nobel Peace Prize 2017: International Campaign to Abolish Nuclear Weapons </b></p><p>Prestigious of all Nobel Prizes, the award for promoting peace is been awarded to the International Campaign to Abolish Nuclear Weapons (ICAN) for their efforts to ban ever piling up nuclear bombs. ICAN is an alliance of non-governmental organizations in more than one hundred countries supporting commitment to and practising of the United Nations nuclear weapon ban treaty, the landmark global agreement adopted in New York on 7 July 2017. </p><p>As of now, it is estimated that there are at least as much as 15,000 potential nuclear weapons present in the arsenal of world countries. The award committee also appreciated the works of the organization to draw attention to the catastrophic humanitarian consequences of any use of nuclear weapons. Setsuko Thurlow, the 85-year-old survivor of 1945 atomic bombing of Hiroshima will jointly accept the Prize together with ICAN’s executive director, Beatrice Fihn, at the Nobel Peace Prize ceremony in Oslo on 10 December. </p><p><b>The Sveriges Riksbank Prize in Economic Sciences in Memory of Alfred Nobel 2017: Richard H. Thaler</b></p><p>The Royal Swedish Academy of Sciences has awarded this year\'s Nobel Prize for Economic Sciences to Richard H. Thaler for his contributions while incorporating economics and psychology. He integrated psychologically realistic assumptions into analyses of economic decision-making. By exploring the consequences of limited rationality, social preferences, and lack of self-control, he has shown how these human traits systematically affect individual decisions as well as market outcomes.</p><p>Thaler is a professor at the University of Chicago and the director of the Center for Decision Research and is the co-director of the Behavioral Economics Project at the National Bureau of Economic Research. Thaler is the co-author of the global bestseller Nudge in which the concepts of behavioural economics are used to tackle many of society’s major problems. In 2015 he published Misbehaving: The Making of Behavioral Economics.</p><p><b>The Nobel Prize in Literature 2017: Kazuo Ishiguro</b></p><p>The Japanese-born British author, Kazuo Ishiguro, was awarded the Nobel Prize in Literature, to quote the Swedish Academy,\"who, in novels of great emotional force, has uncovered the abyss beneath our illusory sense of connection with the world\". As one of the most celebrated English fiction writer in the contemporary world, Kazuo had admitted several times that his Japanese background helped him to look at things in a different perspective. He is the author of Man Booker Prize-winning novel, The Remains of the Day, and his novel, Never Let Me Go, was selected by Time magazine as the best of 2005. </p><p><b>The Nobel Prize in Physiology or Medicine 2017: Jeffrey C. Hall, Michael Rosbash, Michael W. Young</b></p><p>Acknowledging the glory of their discoveries of molecular mechanisms controlling the circadian rhythm, The Nobel Assembly at Karolinska Institute awarded the Nobel Prize in Medicine jointly to Jeffrey C. Hall, Michael Rosbash and Michael W. Young. </p><p>Do you know that living organisms, including humans, have an internal, biological clock that helps them anticipate and adapt to the regular rhythm of the day or the revolutions of our planet? The new Nobel winning trio was able to peek inside these biological clocks and find out its inner workings. Their discoveries explain how plants, animals and humans adapt their biological rhythm so that it is synchronized with the Earth\'s revolutions. They have isolated a gene of fruit flies that controls their normal daily biological rhythm and showed that this gene encodes a protein that accumulates in the cell during the night, and is then degraded during the day. Our wellbeing is affected when there is a temporary mismatch between our external environment and this internal biological clock, for example when we travel across several time zones and experience \"jet lag\". </p><p>Michael Rosbash has been on faculty at Brandeis University in Waltham, USA, since 1974. From 1978, Michael W. Young has been on faculty at the Rockefeller University in New York, while Jeffrey C. Hall is associated with the University of Maine.</p><p><b>The Nobel Prize in Physics 2017: Rainer Weiss, Barry C. Barish, Kip S. Thorne</b></p><p>The Nobel Prize in Physics 2017 was divided, one half awarded to Rainer Weiss, the other half jointly to Barry C. Barish and Kip S. Thorne \"for decisive contributions to the LIGO detector and the observation of gravitational waves\". <span>Rainer Weiss is an American physicist, known for his </span>contributions to<span> gravitational physics and astrophysics. He is a professor of physics emeritus at MIT and an adjunct professor at LSU. He is best known for inventing the laser interferometric technique which is the basic operation of LIGO. He was Chair of the COBE Science Working Group. </span></p><p>Barry Barish is an American experimental physicist. He is a Linde Professor of Physics, emeritus at California Institute of Technology and leading expert on gravitational waves. <span>Kip Stephen Thorne is an American theoretical physicist known for his </span>contributions to<span> gravitational physics and astrophysics. A longtime friend and colleague of Stephen Hawking and Carl Sagan, he was the Feynman Professor of Theoretical Physics at the California Institute of Technology(Caltech) until 2009 and is one of the world\'s leading experts on the astrophysical implications of Einstein\'s general theory of relativity. He continues to do scientific research and scientific consulting, most notably for the Christopher Nolan film Interstellar.</span></p><p><b>The Nobel Prize in Chemistry 2017: Jacques Dubochet, Joachim Frank, Richard Henderson</b></p><p>The Royal Swedish Academy of Sciences has decided to award the Nobel Prize in Chemistry 2017 to <span>Jacques Dubochet, Joachim Frank and Richard Henderson, quoting the academy \"for developing cryo-electron microscopy for the high-resolution structure determination of biomolecules in solution\". </span><span>The development of cryo-electron microscopy may help both in </span>simplifying<span> and </span>improving<span> the images of biomolecules. This method has definitely moved biochemistry into a new era. </span><span>Electron microscopes were long believed to only be suitable for imaging dead </span>matter <span>because the powerful electron beam destroys the </span>biological<span> material. But in 1990, Richard Henderson succeeded in using an electron microscope to generate a three-dimensional image of a protein at atomic resolution. </span></p><p>Jacques Dubochet is an honorary professor of Biophysics at the University of Lausanne, Switzerland. <span>Joachim Frank, German-born professor of Biochemistry and Molecular Biophysics and of Biological Sciences at Columbia University, New York, USA. </span><span>Richard </span>Henderson <span>is a programme Leader at MRC Laboratory of Molecular Biology, Cambridge, UK.</span></p><p><i>The new Nobel Laureates will be honoured in a grant event at Stockholm, Sweden, when they receive the medals and diplomas from King Carl XVI Gustaf of Sweden on December 10, while the Nobel Peace Prize Laureates receive their award from the chairman of Norwegian Nobel Committee in a completely different event held at Oslo, Norway on the same day.</i></p>', '1'),
(66, 5, 'normal', 'MR Vaccine: Kerala Immunises 85% of its children against Measles and Rubella  ', '', 'mrcamp2209201701.jpg', '', '', 'MR Vaccination Campaign is a part of Universal Immunisation Programme under the Union Ministry of Health and Family Welfare launched on February 5, 2017, to eradicate these deadly diseases by vaccinating approximately 41 crore children in the country in a phased manner, thus becoming the largest vaccination campaign attempted anywhere. ', 'Libin Chacko Kurian', '', '2017-11-20', '<div class=\"gmail-OutlineElement gmail-Ltr gmail-SCXW254471758\"><p class=\"gmail-Paragraph gmail-SCXW254471758\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span class=\"gmail-TextRun gmail-SCXW254471758\" lang=\"EN-GB\" >In a mission to eradicate the two deadly diseases</span><span class=\"gmail-TextRun gmail-SCXW254471758\" lang=\"EN-GB\" > measles and rubella, from the country,</span><span class=\"gmail-TextRun gmail-SCXW254471758\" lang=\"EN-GB\" > the state of Kerala has vaccinated 85% of its children, </span><span class=\"gmail-TextRun gmail-SCXW254471758\" lang=\"EN-GB\" >i.e</span><span class=\"gmail-TextRun gmail-SCXW254471758\" lang=\"EN-GB\" >.</span><span class=\"gmail-TextRun gmail-SCXW254471758\" lang=\"EN-GB\" > </span><span class=\"gmail-TextRun gmail-SCXW254471758\" lang=\"EN-GB\" >60 lakh kids between 9 months and 15 </span><span class=\"gmail-TextRun gmail-SCXW254471758\" lang=\"EN-GB\" >years,</span><span class=\"gmail-TextRun gmail-SCXW254471758\" lang=\"EN-GB\" > and</span><span class=\"gmail-TextRun gmail-SCXW254471758\" lang=\"EN-GB\" > has extended the final date till November 25 with an inten</span><span class=\"gmail-TextRun gmail-SCXW254471758\" lang=\"EN-GB\" >ti</span><span class=\"gmail-TextRun gmail-SCXW254471758\" lang=\"EN-GB\" >on to </span><span class=\"gmail-TextRun gmail-SCXW254471758\" lang=\"EN-GB\" >achieve</span><span class=\"gmail-TextRun gmail-SCXW254471758\" lang=\"EN-GB\" > 100% immunisation coverage. As per the data</span><span class=\"gmail-TextRun gmail-SCXW254471758\" lang=\"EN-GB\" > till November 18, as much as 59,66,309 children in the state received MR vaccination in the intensive campaign that started on October 3</span><span class=\"gmail-TextRun gmail-SCXW254471758\" lang=\"EN-GB\" >.</span><span class=\"gmail-TextRun gmail-SCXW254471758\" lang=\"EN-GB\" > The three districts of </span><span class=\"gmail-TextRun gmail-SCXW254471758\" lang=\"EN-GB\" ><span class=\"gmail-SpellingError gmail-SCXW254471758\">Pathanamthitta</span></span><span class=\"gmail-TextRun gmail-SCXW254471758\" lang=\"EN-GB\" >, Kollam an</span><span class=\"gmail-TextRun gmail-SCXW254471758\" lang=\"EN-GB\" >d</span><span class=\"gmail-TextRun gmail-SCXW254471758\" lang=\"EN-GB\" > </span><span class=\"gmail-TextRun gmail-SCXW254471758\" lang=\"EN-GB\" >A</span><span class=\"gmail-TextRun gmail-SCXW254471758\" lang=\"EN-GB\" >lappuzha</span><span class=\"gmail-TextRun gmail-SCXW254471758\" lang=\"EN-GB\" > had successfully completed the campaign with more than 95% of children immunised. </span><span class=\"gmail-TextRun gmail-SCXW254471758\" lang=\"EN-US\" > </span><span class=\"gmail-EOP gmail-SCXW254471758\" > </span></p></div><div class=\"gmail-OutlineElement gmail-Ltr gmail-SCXW254471758\"><p class=\"gmail-Paragraph gmail-SCXW254471758\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span class=\"gmail-TextRun gmail-SCXW254471758\" lang=\"EN-GB\">Measles is a life-</span><span class=\"gmail-TextRun gmail-SCXW254471758\" lang=\"EN-GB\">threatening disease and is one of the major cause</span><span class=\"gmail-TextRun gmail-SCXW254471758\" lang=\"EN-GB\"> of death in children. It is highly contagious and spreads through coughing and sneezing of an infected person. Measles can make a child vulnerable to </span><span class=\"gmail-TextRun gmail-SCXW254471758\" lang=\"EN-GB\">complications such as pneumonia, diarrhoea and brain infection. Globally, in 2015, measles killed an estimated 1, 34,200 children—mostly under-5 years. In India, it killed an estimated 49,200 children. </span><span class=\"gmail-TextRun gmail-SCXW254471758\" lang=\"EN-US\"> </span><span class=\"gmail-EOP gmail-SCXW254471758\"> </span></p></div><div class=\"gmail-OutlineElement gmail-Ltr gmail-SCXW254471758\"><p class=\"gmail-Paragraph gmail-SCXW254471758\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span class=\"gmail-TextRun gmail-SCXW254471758\" lang=\"EN-GB\">Rubella is generally a mild infection but has serious consequences if infection occurs in pregnant women, causing congenital rubella syndrome (CRS), which is a cause of public health concern. CRS is characterized by congenital anomalies in the foetus and </span><span class=\"gmail-TextRun gmail-SCXW254471758\" lang=\"EN-GB\">new-borns</span><span class=\"gmail-TextRun gmail-SCXW254471758\" lang=\"EN-GB\"> affecting the eyes (glaucoma, cataract), ears (hearing loss), brain (microcephaly, mental retardation) and heart defects, causing a huge socioeconomic burden on the families and society</span><span class=\"gmail-TextRun gmail-SCXW254471758\" lang=\"EN-GB\">. </span><span class=\"gmail-TextRun gmail-SCXW254471758\" lang=\"EN-US\"> </span><span class=\"gmail-EOP gmail-SCXW254471758\"> </span></p></div><div class=\"gmail-OutlineElement gmail-Ltr gmail-SCXW254471758\"><p class=\"gmail-Paragraph gmail-SCXW254471758\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span class=\"gmail-TextRun gmail-SCXW254471758\" lang=\"EN-GB\">The state has </span><span class=\"gmail-TextRun gmail-SCXW254471758\" lang=\"EN-GB\">trained caregivers, school teachers, Anganwadi workers and frontline health workers for this campaign, while also had parallel counselling and </span><span class=\"gmail-TextRun gmail-SCXW254471758\" lang=\"EN-GB\">awareness</span><span class=\"gmail-TextRun gmail-SCXW254471758\" lang=\"EN-GB\"> programs to attract parents and the general public. The original plan was to achieve 100% coverage by November 3 through an intensive campaign. But the vaccination programme was destined to face several challenges and had to postpone the final date until 18 November, which now again got extended till November 25. The government has asked schools, health centres and hospitals to </span><span class=\"gmail-TextRun gmail-SCXW254471758\" lang=\"EN-GB\">continue</span><span class=\"gmail-TextRun gmail-SCXW254471758\" lang=\"EN-GB\"> vaccination even after the deadline to achieve total vaccination and complete er</span><span class=\"gmail-TextRun gmail-SCXW254471758\" lang=\"EN-GB\">adication</span><span class=\"gmail-TextRun gmail-SCXW254471758\" lang=\"EN-GB\"> of these </span><span class=\"gmail-TextRun gmail-SCXW254471758\" lang=\"EN-GB\">diseases</span><span class=\"gmail-TextRun gmail-SCXW254471758\" lang=\"EN-GB\">. </span><span class=\"gmail-TextRun gmail-SCXW254471758\" lang=\"EN-US\"> </span><span class=\"gmail-EOP gmail-SCXW254471758\"> </span></p></div><div class=\"gmail-OutlineElement gmail-Ltr gmail-SCXW254471758\"><p class=\"gmail-Paragraph gmail-SCXW254471758\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span class=\"gmail-TextRun gmail-SCXW254471758\" lang=\"EN-GB\">MR Vaccination Campaign is a part of Universal Immunisation Programme under the U</span><span class=\"gmail-TextRun gmail-SCXW254471758\" lang=\"EN-GB\">nion M</span><span class=\"gmail-TextRun gmail-SCXW254471758\" lang=\"EN-GB\">inistry of Health and F</span><span class=\"gmail-TextRun gmail-SCXW254471758\" lang=\"EN-GB\">amily </span><span class=\"gmail-TextRun gmail-SCXW254471758\" lang=\"EN-GB\">Welfare launched</span><span class=\"gmail-TextRun gmail-SCXW254471758\" lang=\"EN-GB\"> on February 5, 2017, to eradicate these deadly diseases by vaccinating approximately 41 crore children in the country in a phased </span><span class=\"gmail-TextRun gmail-SCXW254471758\" lang=\"EN-GB\">manner, t</span><span class=\"gmail-TextRun gmail-SCXW254471758\" lang=\"EN-GB\">hus</span><span class=\"gmail-TextRun gmail-SCXW254471758\" lang=\"EN-GB\"> becoming the largest vaccination </span><span class=\"gmail-TextRun gmail-SCXW254471758\" lang=\"EN-GB\">campaign</span><span class=\"gmail-TextRun gmail-SCXW254471758\" lang=\"EN-GB\"> </span><span class=\"gmail-TextRun gmail-SCXW254471758\" lang=\"EN-GB\">attempted anywhere</span><span class=\"gmail-TextRun gmail-SCXW254471758\" lang=\"EN-GB\">.</span><span class=\"gmail-TextRun gmail-SCXW254471758\" lang=\"EN-GB\"> </span><span class=\"gmail-TextRun gmail-SCXW254471758\" lang=\"EN-GB\">During the first </span><span class=\"gmail-TextRun gmail-SCXW254471758\" lang=\"EN-GB\">phase, the states Tamil</span><span class=\"gmail-TextRun gmail-SCXW254471758\" lang=\"EN-GB\"> Nadu, K</span><span class=\"gmail-TextRun gmail-SCXW254471758\" lang=\"EN-GB\">arnataka, Goa, </span><span class=\"gmail-TextRun gmail-SCXW254471758\" lang=\"EN-GB\">Pondicherry</span><span class=\"gmail-TextRun gmail-SCXW254471758\" lang=\"EN-GB\"> and </span><span class=\"gmail-TextRun gmail-SCXW254471758\" lang=\"EN-GB\">Lakshadweep</span><span class=\"gmail-TextRun gmail-SCXW254471758\" lang=\"EN-GB\"> had already vaccinated around 3.32 crore children until March 31, 2017. </span><span class=\"gmail-TextRun gmail-SCXW254471758\" lang=\"EN-GB\">The second p</span><span class=\"gmail-TextRun gmail-SCXW254471758\" lang=\"EN-GB\">hase that started in early October is anticipated to cover 3.4 crore </span><span class=\"gmail-TextRun gmail-SCXW254471758\" lang=\"EN-GB\">children</span><span class=\"gmail-TextRun gmail-SCXW254471758\" lang=\"EN-GB\"> spread across eight states including Kerala. </span><span class=\"gmail-TextRun gmail-SCXW254471758\" lang=\"EN-GB\">After </span><span class=\"gmail-TextRun gmail-SCXW254471758\" lang=\"EN-GB\">completion of this campaign, MR vaccine will replace the Measles v</span><span class=\"gmail-TextRun gmail-SCXW254471758\" lang=\"EN-GB\">accine and will a part of routine Immunis</span><span class=\"gmail-TextRun gmail-SCXW254471758\" lang=\"EN-GB\">ation soon. </span><span class=\"gmail-TextRun gmail-SCXW254471758\" lang=\"EN-US\"> </span><span class=\"gmail-EOP gmail-SCXW254471758\"> </span></p></div><div class=\"gmail-OutlineElement gmail-Ltr gmail-SCXW254471758\"><p class=\"gmail-Paragraph gmail-SCXW254471758\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span class=\"gmail-TextRun gmail-SCXW254471758\" lang=\"EN-GB\">Polio, Meas</span><span class=\"gmail-TextRun gmail-SCXW254471758\" lang=\"EN-GB\">les</span><span class=\"gmail-TextRun gmail-SCXW254471758\" lang=\"EN-GB\"> and Rubella are the only three </span><span class=\"gmail-TextRun gmail-SCXW254471758\" lang=\"EN-GB\">diseases</span><span class=\"gmail-TextRun gmail-SCXW254471758\" lang=\"EN-GB\"> transmitted by humans and </span><span class=\"gmail-TextRun gmail-SCXW254471758\" lang=\"EN-GB\">only</span><span class=\"gmail-TextRun gmail-SCXW254471758\" lang=\"EN-GB\"> found in human beings. </span><span class=\"gmail-TextRun gmail-SCXW254471758\" lang=\"EN-GB\">So,</span><span class=\"gmail-TextRun gmail-SCXW254471758\" lang=\"EN-GB\"> it is viable to eradicate the disease if proper vaccination is received in right time. </span><span class=\"gmail-TextRun gmail-SCXW254471758\" lang=\"EN-US\"> </span><span class=\"gmail-EOP gmail-SCXW254471758\"> </span></p></div>', '1'),
(67, 4, 'normal', 'Uber and NASA to Fly \'Air Taxis\' by 2020: 5 Things You Should Know  ', '', 'uberelevate.jpg', '', '', '\'Uber Elevate\' is an ambitious program designed by the biggest taxi service provider on the planet to develop a future air transport system using \'flying cars\' to move commuters between sky ports.  ', 'Db correspondent', '', '2017-11-21', '<div><b><span >1. Uber is teaming up with NASA</span><br></b></div><div class=\"OutlineElement Ltr SCXW37155703\"><p class=\"Paragraph SCXW37155703\"><span class=\"TextRun SCXW37155703\" lang=\"EN-GB\">To develop a brand-new air traffic management system, Uber has signed a Space Act Agreement with N</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW37155703\" lang=\"EN-GB\">ational Aeronautics and Space Administration (NASA)</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW37155703\" lang=\"EN-GB\"> of U</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW37155703\" lang=\"EN-GB\">nited States. NASA is into building a basic framework and is expected to provide </span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW37155703\" lang=\"EN-GB\">lo</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW37155703\" lang=\"EN-GB\">gical</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW37155703\" lang=\"EN-GB\"> support to manage the low flying, </span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW37155703\" lang=\"EN-GB\">autonomous</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW37155703\" lang=\"EN-GB\"><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW37155703\"> </span></span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW37155703\" lang=\"EN-GB\">aerial</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW37155703\" lang=\"EN-GB\"> taxi service. </span></p><p class=\"Paragraph SCXW37155703\"><b><span class=\"TextRun SCXW37155703\" lang=\"EN-GB\">2. Aircrafts are designed to move vertically</span><span class=\"EOP SCXW37155703\" data-ccp-props=\"{\"> </span></b></p></div><div class=\"OutlineElement Ltr SCXW37155703\"><p class=\"Paragraph SCXW37155703\"><span class=\"TextRun SCXW37155703\" lang=\"EN-GB\">\'Electric Vertical </span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW37155703\" lang=\"EN-GB\">Take-O</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW37155703\" lang=\"EN-GB\">ff</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW37155703\" lang=\"EN-GB\"> and L</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW37155703\" lang=\"EN-GB\">anding </span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW37155703\" lang=\"EN-GB\">Vehicles\' (</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW37155703\" lang=\"EN-GB\">EV</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW37155703\" lang=\"EN-GB\">TO</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW37155703\" lang=\"EN-GB\">Ls) are specially designed aircrafts visualised by Uber with the ability to take-off and land vertically, which may move from rooftop to rooftop of tall buildings. As the technology for such </span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW37155703\" lang=\"EN-GB\">infrastructure</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW37155703\" lang=\"EN-GB\"> doesn\'t exist yet, the </span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW37155703\" lang=\"EN-GB\">sceptics</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW37155703\" lang=\"EN-GB\"><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW37155703\"> </span></span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW37155703\" lang=\"EN-GB\">say, </span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW37155703\" lang=\"EN-GB\">the</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW37155703\" lang=\"EN-GB\"> company will transcend the current operating methods, if the project succeeds. </span></p><p class=\"Paragraph SCXW37155703\"><b><span class=\"TextRun SCXW37155703\" lang=\"EN-GB\">3. The </span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW37155703\" lang=\"EN-GB\">aircrafts</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW37155703\" lang=\"EN-GB\"> will soar in sky with 322 </span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW37155703\" lang=\"EN-GB\"><span class=\"SpellingError SCXW37155703\">Kmph</span></span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW37155703\" lang=\"EN-GB\">  speed</span><span class=\"EOP SCXW37155703\" data-ccp-props=\"{\"> </span></b></p></div><div class=\"OutlineElement Ltr SCXW37155703\"><p class=\"Paragraph SCXW37155703\"><span class=\"TextRun SCXW37155703\" lang=\"EN-GB\"> As the company claims, EVTOLs can fly at a maximum speed of 322 </span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW37155703\" lang=\"EN-GB\"><span class=\"SpellingError SCXW37155703\">Kmph</span></span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW37155703\" lang=\"EN-GB\"> and finish off a trip in 15 </span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW37155703\" lang=\"EN-GB\">minut</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW37155703\" lang=\"EN-GB\">es</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW37155703\" lang=\"EN-GB\">, that may otherwise take an hour and a half to complete. The company is taking advantage of the space above urban </span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW37155703\" lang=\"EN-GB\">cent</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW37155703\" lang=\"EN-GB\">res</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW37155703\" lang=\"EN-GB\"> to reduce congestion on the ground and to make cities more open and </span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW37155703\" lang=\"EN-GB\">accessible</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW37155703\" lang=\"EN-GB\"> for everyone. </span><span class=\"EOP SCXW37155703\" data-ccp-props=\"{\"> </span></p><p class=\"Paragraph SCXW37155703\"><b><span class=\"TextRun SCXW37155703\" lang=\"EN-GB\">4. The three cities lucky to have first \'flying cars\'</span><span class=\"EOP SCXW37155703\" data-ccp-props=\"{\"> </span></b></p></div><div class=\"OutlineElement Ltr SCXW37155703\"><p class=\"Paragraph SCXW37155703\"><span class=\"TextRun SCXW37155703\" lang=\"EN-GB\">Dallas – Fort Worth, Dubai and Los </span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW37155703\" lang=\"EN-GB\">Angele</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW37155703\" lang=\"EN-GB\">s</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW37155703\" lang=\"EN-GB\"> are the three global cities fortunate enough to have the \'flying cars\'</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW37155703\" lang=\"EN-GB\"> on their skies as announced by Uber. The aerial taxi is anticipated to pilot the services by 2020 in these cities. The urban </span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW37155703\" lang=\"EN-GB\">cent</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW37155703\" lang=\"EN-GB\">res</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW37155703\" lang=\"EN-GB\"> are </span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW37155703\" lang=\"EN-GB\">selected</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW37155703\" lang=\"EN-GB\"> according to the traffic congestion and time management pressures they face today. </span><span class=\"EOP SCXW37155703\" data-ccp-props=\"{\"> </span></p><p class=\"Paragraph SCXW37155703\"><b><span class=\"TextRun SCXW37155703\" lang=\"EN-GB\">5. Full-</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW37155703\" lang=\"EN-GB\">fledged</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW37155703\" lang=\"EN-GB\"> operations before \'Los Angeles </span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW37155703\" lang=\"EN-GB\">Olympics\' </span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW37155703\" lang=\"EN-GB\">2028</span><span class=\"EOP SCXW37155703\" data-ccp-props=\"{\"> </span></b></p></div><div class=\"OutlineElement Ltr SCXW37155703\"><p class=\"Paragraph SCXW37155703\"><span class=\"TextRun SCXW37155703\" lang=\"EN-GB\">Ten years from now, Uber envisions of getting air taxi operational before the Los Angeles Olympics of 2028. </span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW37155703\" lang=\"EN-GB\"> The forthcoming </span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW37155703\" lang=\"EN-GB\">multi-</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW37155703\" lang=\"EN-GB\">sport</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW37155703\" lang=\"EN-GB\"> event, the summer O</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW37155703\" lang=\"EN-GB\">lympics of 2028 will be held in the city of Los Angeles, California, the USA between July 21 and August 6, 2028. As one of the most traffic affected the city on the planet, EVTOLs are looking forward to easing the vehicle mobility and speed travelling. </span><span class=\"EOP SCXW37155703\" data-ccp-props=\"{\"> </span></p></div><div class=\"OutlineElement Ltr SCXW37155703\"><p class=\"Paragraph SCXW37155703\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span class=\"TextRun SCXW37155703\" lang=\"EN-GB\">J</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW37155703\" lang=\"EN-GB\">eff Holden, Chief Product O</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW37155703\" lang=\"EN-GB\">fficer, Uber </span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW37155703\" lang=\"EN-GB\">says </span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW37155703\" lang=\"EN-GB\">\"So </span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW37155703\" lang=\"EN-GB\">far,</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW37155703\" lang=\"EN-GB\"> we have been focusing on ground-based transportation and for us, the natural next step </span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW37155703\" lang=\"EN-GB\">is </span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW37155703\" lang=\"EN-GB\">flying</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW37155703\" lang=\"EN-GB\">. Flying can really replace driving as in many cases it is taking people\'s precious </span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW37155703\" lang=\"EN-GB\">time </span>and it<span class=\"TextRun SCXW37155703\" lang=\"EN-GB\"></span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW37155703\" lang=\"EN-GB\"> can be done in a way that is </span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW37155703\" lang=\"EN-GB\">ultimately</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW37155703\" lang=\"EN-GB\"><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW37155703\"> </span></span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW37155703\" lang=\"EN-GB\">less</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW37155703\" lang=\"EN-GB\"> expensive than car ownership </span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW37155703\" lang=\"EN-GB\">as</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW37155703\" lang=\"EN-GB\"> well as friendly to </span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW37155703\" lang=\"EN-GB\">environm</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW37155703\" lang=\"EN-GB\">e</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW37155703\" lang=\"EN-GB\">nt</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW37155703\" lang=\"EN-GB\"> and community. But the big win is time-saving. Trips that can take hours on the ground can be reduced to minutes in the air. </span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW37155703\" lang=\"EN-GB\">Giving time back to people is something we are very passionate about in Uber. That\'s more time with family, more time for growing our </span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW37155703\" lang=\"EN-GB\">economy</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW37155703\" lang=\"EN-GB\"> and lower stress for everyone.</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW37155703\" lang=\"EN-GB\">\" </span><span class=\"EOP SCXW37155703\" data-ccp-props=\"{\"> </span></p></div>', '1'),
(68, 17, 'normal', 'I LIKE SPRING,  BECAUSE YOU MADE IT SO', 'Alappadu', 'IMG20171031101039.jpg', '', '', '', 'Aswathy Achu                                        ', '', '2017-10-31', '<div dir=\"auto\" >I like spring, because you made it so.</div><div dir=\"auto\" ><br></div><div dir=\"auto\" >you gave the name, you made the showers.</div><div dir=\"auto\" ><br></div><div dir=\"auto\" >you put the dew on my eyelids.</div><div dir=\"auto\" ><br></div><div dir=\"auto\" >and from you the season came.</div><div dir=\"auto\" ><br></div><div dir=\"auto\" >The rhythm of the season reached my ears,</div><div dir=\"auto\" ><br></div><div dir=\"auto\" >with its blooming buds of love.</div><div dir=\"auto\" ><br></div><div dir=\"auto\" >lily, Jasmine and the queenliest rose</div><div dir=\"auto\" ><br></div><div dir=\"auto\" >ran into the queue, made the bouquet.</div><div dir=\"auto\" ><br></div><div dir=\"auto\" >The garland you made with passion</div><div dir=\"auto\" ><br></div><div dir=\"auto\" >made me a bride,&nbsp;</div><div dir=\"auto\" ><br></div><div dir=\"auto\" >within the braids, it seems like an apparition on the sky</div><div dir=\"auto\" ><br></div><div dir=\"auto\" >telling my future, the next spring.</div><div dir=\"auto\" ><br></div><div dir=\"auto\" >who made thine eyes? vaster than the sea, brighter than a pearl, reflects mine.</div><div dir=\"auto\" ><br></div><div dir=\"auto\" >it makes me fall into it and die</div><div dir=\"auto\" ><br></div><div dir=\"auto\" >towards the empire of eternity.</div>', '1'),
(69, 4, 'normal', 'ISRO to double its launching frequency to 20 satellites in a year: Chairman ', '', 'images2.jpeg', '', '', 'India is poised to become a front-runner among the World’s space program by fostering partnerships in the friendly South Asian countries along with Russia and Japan which further translates towards the creation of a huge pool of high-value high-wage jobs in various advanced technology sectors.', 'Db correspondent ', '', '2017-11-22', '<p>In a two-day International Seminar on “Indian Space Programme\" held at New Delhi on November 20, 2017, ISRO Chairman, AS Kiran Kumar, announced that the agency will soon be doubling its launching frequency from 9-10 to about 20 in a year. The event organised by FICCI also saw the launch of a Space Compendium, which showcases the products and services available in Space and Satellite industry in India for greater cooperation in B2B and B2G space.</p><p>AS Kiran Kumar, Chairman, ISRO said “World of space is rapidly changing with technological advancements and disruptive innovation. Key to success is to significantly reduce the cost of access to space in what will prove to be an immense opportunity for the Indian and global industry”. He also mentioned that ‘space industry in India is significantly short of capacity for our intended goals’. He emphasised the fact that with increasing volumes that are on offer by ISRO and other Space Agencies, it is an ideal opportunity for the industry to be part of the global supply chain.</p><p>The prognosis for Indian industry looks particularly bright with the immense benefits emanating from a developed space ecosystem which directly augment such widely impacting sectors such as Telecommunications, GIS, Agriculture, Meteorology, Mining and Natural resource conservation. This further translates towards creation of a huge pool of high value-high wage jobs in various advanced technology sectors<br></p><p>Ratan Shrivastava, Honorary Advisor, FICCI Space Division said “ISRO is the true flag bearer of the Make In India statement and almost 80% of the work related to Launch vehicles is being done by the Industry, both in public and private sector, which allows ISRO to focus on the core areas of vehicle engineering, vehicle integration, mission systems and Quality Assurance.”</p><p>HS Shankar, Chairman, FICCI Space Committee, mentioned that ISRO and the Industry share a Guru-Disciple relationship, where ISRO has played the role of a guide to Indian space industry by hand-holding and mentoring the upcoming and nascent private space and satellite industry. He lauded ISRO for involving more than over a hundred MSMEs as active participants in their programmes. He also stated that “For cooperation in space, Sky is not the limit.”&nbsp;</p><p><br></p>', '1'),
(70, 5, 'normal', 'In the midst of migratory season, Kochi to go for a bird spotting race this Sunday ', 'Kochi', 'YellowFootedGreenPigeon2921.jpg', 'Yellow Footed Green Pigeon. Pic by Vishnupriyan Kartha, Secretary, Cochin Natural History Society.', '', 'The contestants will meet to share experiences of the day, cross-check and collate the sightings, determine which of the commonest birds missed, which of the rarest ones and who were the lucky to spot etc., with fellow travellers. The event is open to the public including students and is without any registration fees. ', 'Libin Chacko Kurian ', '', '2017-11-22', '<div dir=\"ltr\"><div class=\"OutlineElement Ltr SCXW212664036\" ><p class=\"Paragraph SCXW212664036\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\" paraid=\"476691211\" paraeid=\"{d76a65d8-44df-4034-aafc-4eaa2b7ed686}{77}\" ><span class=\"TextRun SCXW212664036\" xml:lang=\"EN-GB\" lang=\"EN-GB\" ><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW212664036\" >As the winter already started and birds are having their migratory season, Cochin Natural History Society (CNHS) is organising the Kerala Bird Race 2017 at Kochi and outskirts on November 26 in its eleventh iteration. The Bird Race -though it has a competitive tone in it- is not a race yet encourages to push the limits to watch, listen, experience and record as many as birds during the course of a day. The participants can record their bird sightings on&nbsp;</span></span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW212664036\" xml:lang=\"EN-GB\" lang=\"EN-GB\" ><span class=\"SpellingError SCXW212664036\" >eBird</span></span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW212664036\" xml:lang=\"EN-GB\" lang=\"EN-GB\" ><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW212664036\" >&nbsp;Website using the&nbsp;</span></span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW212664036\" xml:lang=\"EN-GB\" lang=\"EN-GB\" ><span class=\"SpellingError SCXW212664036\" >eBird</span></span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW212664036\" xml:lang=\"EN-GB\" lang=\"EN-GB\" ><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW212664036\" >&nbsp;mobile App. After a hectic day of birding in the surrounding areas of Kochi city and outskirts- up to 50 km radius- the contestants will meet at a suitable place to share experiences of the day, cross-check and collate the sightings, determine which of the commonest birds missed; which of the rarest ones and who were the lucky to spot etc., with fellow travellers.</span></span><span class=\"EOP SCXW212664036\" data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\" >&nbsp;</span></p></div><div class=\"OutlineElement Ltr SCXW212664036\" ><p class=\"Paragraph SCXW212664036\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\" paraid=\"1027441499\" paraeid=\"{d76a65d8-44df-4034-aafc-4eaa2b7ed686}{81}\" ><span class=\"TextRun SCXW212664036\" xml:lang=\"EN-GB\" lang=\"EN-GB\" ><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW212664036\" >Birds always fascinate and intrigue us with their colours, shapes, songs, calls and their&nbsp;</span></span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW212664036\" xml:lang=\"EN-GB\" lang=\"EN-GB\" ><span class=\"SpellingError SCXW212664036\" >jizz</span></span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW212664036\" xml:lang=\"EN-GB\" lang=\"EN-GB\" ><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW212664036\" >&nbsp;which can move the hearts of even driest of the&nbsp;</span></span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW212664036\" xml:lang=\"EN-GB\" lang=\"EN-GB\" ><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW212664036\" >humans.&nbsp;We</span></span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW212664036\" xml:lang=\"EN-GB\" lang=\"EN-GB\" ><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW212664036\" >&nbsp;are in the midst of the migratory birding season and now we can see many winged beauties in monochromes, duo tones and multicolour-&nbsp;</span></span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW212664036\" xml:lang=\"EN-GB\" lang=\"EN-GB\" ><span class=\"SpellingError SCXW212664036\" >vibgyor</span></span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW212664036\" xml:lang=\"EN-GB\" lang=\"EN-GB\" ><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW212664036\" >, both occurring throughout the year in our state and those who come to visit and&nbsp;</span></span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW212664036\" xml:lang=\"EN-GB\" lang=\"EN-GB\" ><span class=\"SpellingError SCXW212664036\" >enthrall</span></span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW212664036\" xml:lang=\"EN-GB\" lang=\"EN-GB\" ><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW212664036\" >&nbsp;us with the myriad hues and huge repertoire of songs from other parts of the globe during this time of the year. The Bird Race with its fun element is the perfect reason and time to observe and enjoy the beauties in the company of our friends, family or expert birders.</span></span><span class=\"EOP SCXW212664036\" data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\" >&nbsp;</span></p></div><div class=\"OutlineElement Ltr SCXW212664036\" ><p class=\"Paragraph SCXW212664036\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\" paraid=\"1485542592\" paraeid=\"{d76a65d8-44df-4034-aafc-4eaa2b7ed686}{85}\" ><b><span class=\"TextRun SCXW212664036\" xml:lang=\"EN-GB\" lang=\"EN-GB\" ><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW212664036\" >Training Session</span></span><span class=\"EOP SCXW212664036\" data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\" >&nbsp;</span></b></p></div><div class=\"OutlineElement Ltr SCXW212664036\" ><p class=\"Paragraph SCXW212664036\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\" paraid=\"193184231\" paraeid=\"{d76a65d8-44df-4034-aafc-4eaa2b7ed686}{87}\" ><span class=\"TextRun SCXW212664036\" xml:lang=\"EN-GB\" lang=\"EN-GB\" ><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW212664036\" >The event will also have a briefing session for new birdwatchers and experienced ones to interact with each other on the previous day of the race- at&nbsp;</span></span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW212664036\" xml:lang=\"EN-GB\" lang=\"EN-GB\" ><span class=\"SpellingError SCXW212664036\" >Mangalavanam</span></span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW212664036\" xml:lang=\"EN-GB\" lang=\"EN-GB\" ><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW212664036\" >&nbsp;Bird Sanctuary at 5 pm on Saturday, November 25.</span></span><span class=\"EOP SCXW212664036\" data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\" >&nbsp;</span></p></div></div>', '1'),
(71, 17, 'normal', 'She ', 'Alappad', 'images3.jpeg', '', '', '', 'Ashwathy Achu', '', '2017-11-02', '<div dir=\"auto\" >Some day earth will cease its motion.</div><div dir=\"auto\" ><br></div><div dir=\"auto\" >Scattered planets will be there.</div><div dir=\"auto\" ><br></div><div dir=\"auto\" >Who cares the sun?</div><div dir=\"auto\" ><br></div><div dir=\"auto\" >Let him burn,</div><div dir=\"auto\" >Burn into ashes<br></div><div dir=\"auto\" >Before he attack the stars</div><div dir=\"auto\" >Whom he feels inferior to him.</div><div dir=\"auto\" ><br></div><div dir=\"auto\" >Who called the sun \'he\'?</div><div dir=\"auto\" >Why cant it be a \'she\'?</div><div dir=\"auto\" >With gorgeous wings of fire</div><div dir=\"auto\" >In her bright burning skin</div><div dir=\"auto\" >Moves golden flakes of beauty</div><div dir=\"auto\" >Makes her prettier than ever.</div><div dir=\"auto\" ><br></div><div dir=\"auto\" >She is \'sun\'</div><div dir=\"auto\" ><br></div><div dir=\"auto\" >Like a forbidden fruit above there</div><div dir=\"auto\" >As precious as a piece of ruby</div><div dir=\"auto\" >Wipes away the darkness in minds.</div><div dir=\"auto\" ><br></div><div dir=\"auto\" >She moves from east to west</div><div dir=\"auto\" >Hides herself beneath the horizon</div><div dir=\"auto\" >So Ends a day.</div><div dir=\"auto\" >Her brightness might cheat her</div><div dir=\"auto\" >But her boldness won\'t .</div><div dir=\"auto\" ><br></div><div dir=\"auto\" >Let her not hide.</div><div dir=\"auto\" >Let her rise and shine.</div><div dir=\"auto\" >_____</div><div dir=\"auto\" ><br></div><div dir=\"auto\" >Some day earth will cease its motion.</div><div dir=\"auto\" ><br></div><div dir=\"auto\" >Scattered planets will be there.</div><div dir=\"auto\" ><br></div><div dir=\"auto\" >Who cares the sun?</div><div dir=\"auto\" ><br></div><div dir=\"auto\" >Let him burn,</div><div dir=\"auto\" >Burn into ashes<br></div><div dir=\"auto\" >Before he attack the stars</div><div dir=\"auto\" >Whom he feels inferior to him.</div><div dir=\"auto\" ><br></div><div dir=\"auto\" >Who called the sun \'he\'?</div><div dir=\"auto\" >Why cant it be a \'she\'?</div><div dir=\"auto\" >With gorgeous wings of fire</div><div dir=\"auto\" >In her bright burning skin</div><div dir=\"auto\" >Moves golden flakes of beauty</div><div dir=\"auto\" >Makes her prettier than ever.</div><div dir=\"auto\" ><br></div><div dir=\"auto\" >She is \'sun\'</div><div dir=\"auto\" ><br></div><div dir=\"auto\" >Like a forbidden fruit above there</div><div dir=\"auto\" >As precious as a piece of ruby</div><div dir=\"auto\" >Wipes away the darkness in minds.</div><div dir=\"auto\" ><br></div><div dir=\"auto\" >She moves from east to west</div><div dir=\"auto\" >Hides herself beneath the horizon</div><div dir=\"auto\" >So Ends a day.</div><div dir=\"auto\" >Her brightness might cheat her</div><div dir=\"auto\" >But her boldness won\'t .</div><div dir=\"auto\" ><br></div><div dir=\"auto\" >Let her not hide.</div><div dir=\"auto\" >Let her rise and shine.</div>', '1'),
(72, 17, 'normal', 'Drown ', 'Alappad', 'images4.jpeg', '', '', '', 'Ashwathy Achu', '', '2017-11-10', '<div dir=\"auto\" >Empty turns to full;</div><div dir=\"auto\" ><br></div><div dir=\"auto\" >Emptiness to Content.</div><div dir=\"auto\" ><br></div><div dir=\"auto\" >Pebbles, weeds and mud</div><div dir=\"auto\" ><br></div><div dir=\"auto\" >tiny ticklish fishes moving</div><div dir=\"auto\" ><br></div><div dir=\"auto\" >into the darkest realm.</div><div dir=\"auto\" ><br></div><div dir=\"auto\" >scars are plenty with thorns</div><div dir=\"auto\" ><br></div><div dir=\"auto\" >draws some red forest</div><div dir=\"auto\" ><br></div><div dir=\"auto\" >through the lines of life.</div><div dir=\"auto\" ><br></div><div dir=\"auto\" >My palm bleeds, I laugh.</div><div dir=\"auto\" ><br></div><div dir=\"auto\" >water seems thicker, so&nbsp;</div><div dir=\"auto\" ><br></div><div dir=\"auto\" >it disagrees to dissolve the redness.</div><div dir=\"auto\" ><br></div><div dir=\"auto\" >it flows like a dizzy man</div><div dir=\"auto\" ><br></div><div dir=\"auto\" >who stands between the two shores.</div><div dir=\"auto\" ><br></div><div dir=\"auto\" >some unnamed ambhibian</div><div dir=\"auto\" ><br></div><div dir=\"auto\" >plucked my eyeballs, I wink.</div><div dir=\"auto\" ><br></div><div dir=\"auto\" >the silky threads begin to grey</div><div dir=\"auto\" ><br></div><div dir=\"auto\" >will no more shine like before.</div><div dir=\"auto\" ><br></div><div dir=\"auto\" >thr brushes wet,</div><div dir=\"auto\" ><br></div><div dir=\"auto\" >left the canvas red,</div><div dir=\"auto\" ><br></div><div dir=\"auto\" >He paused.</div><div><br></div>', '1');
