(73, 17, 'normal', 'Waiting ', 'Alappad', 'images5.jpeg', '', '', '', 'Ashwathy Achu', '', '2017-11-15', '<div dir=\"auto\" >￼Who are you?</div><div dir=\"auto\" ><br></div><div dir=\"auto\" >Are you the one</div><div dir=\"auto\" >Who has been waiting for me?</div><div dir=\"auto\" ><br></div><div dir=\"auto\" >Or the one who wants</div><div dir=\"auto\" ><br></div><div dir=\"auto\" >Me to wait for?</div><div dir=\"auto\" ><br></div><div dir=\"auto\" >Like Sita did for Raman</div><div dir=\"auto\" ><br></div><div dir=\"auto\" >In the solitude of a hermitage.</div><div dir=\"auto\" ><br></div><div dir=\"auto\" >Like seasons did for spring,</div><div dir=\"auto\" ><br></div><div dir=\"auto\" >Even it lost hope in a drought.</div><div dir=\"auto\" ><br></div><div dir=\"auto\" >Like seashore did for a new tide</div><div dir=\"auto\" ><br></div><div dir=\"auto\" >When it refuses to come back.</div><div dir=\"auto\" ><br></div><div dir=\"auto\" >Oh?!</div><div dir=\"auto\" ><br></div><div dir=\"auto\" >Fool you are.</div><div dir=\"auto\" ><br></div><div dir=\"auto\" >Do not suspect me.</div><div dir=\"auto\" ><br></div><div dir=\"auto\" >It’s you made me&nbsp;</div><div dir=\"auto\" ><br></div><div dir=\"auto\" >Who i am.</div><div dir=\"auto\" ><br></div><div dir=\"auto\" >How far this longing take?</div><div dir=\"auto\" ><br></div><div dir=\"auto\" >Years?</div><div dir=\"auto\" ><br></div><div dir=\"auto\" >Centuries?</div><div dir=\"auto\" ><br></div><div dir=\"auto\" >It is good to wait for you</div><div dir=\"auto\" ><br></div><div dir=\"auto\" >When it is sure that&nbsp;</div><div dir=\"auto\" ><br></div><div dir=\"auto\" >You will return.</div><div dir=\"auto\" ><br></div><div dir=\"auto\" >Come back soon</div><div dir=\"auto\" ><br></div><div dir=\"auto\" >With the soul&nbsp;</div><div dir=\"auto\" ><br></div><div dir=\"auto\" >That you have stolen from me.</div><div dir=\"auto\" ><br></div><div dir=\"auto\" >I know you will</div><div dir=\"auto\" ><br></div><div dir=\"auto\" >And me too.</div>', '1'),
(74, 17, 'normal', 'The Vulnerable', 'Alappad', 'images6.jpeg', '', '', '', 'Ashwathy Achu', '', '2017-11-22', '<div dir=\"auto\" >Hurt by the knife of silence,</div><div dir=\"auto\" >Her insane heart tend to bleed.</div><div dir=\"auto\" >The dark red flow of pain</div><div dir=\"auto\" >Travelled through the valley of violence.</div><div dir=\"auto\" ><br></div><div dir=\"auto\" >Ever they noticed the girl&nbsp;</div><div dir=\"auto\" >Who had the brightest eyes</div><div dir=\"auto\" >Gorgeous face, burning skin</div><div dir=\"auto\" >With shining light of a pearl?</div><div dir=\"auto\" ><br></div><div dir=\"auto\" >Never!</div><div dir=\"auto\" >They hardly lend their ears</div><div dir=\"auto\" >Towards the creepy mourns</div><div dir=\"auto\" >And each day they enjoyed</div><div dir=\"auto\" >Breaking her fences into tears.</div><div dir=\"auto\" ><br></div><div dir=\"auto\" >I am indebted to you my patron&nbsp;</div><div dir=\"auto\" >For pulling me out of them.</div><div dir=\"auto\" >Without diminishing the grace of muses</div><div dir=\"auto\" >To create letters that are golden.</div><div dir=\"auto\" ><br></div><div dir=\"auto\" >Some day she will stop moving,</div><div dir=\"auto\" >Break the galaxy and cry aloud</div><div dir=\"auto\" >Will man realise his deeds even then?</div><div dir=\"auto\" >Or step into her head and keep laughing?</div>', '1'),
(75, 4, 'normal', '5 Facts You Must Know About Sophia, The First Robot To Own A Citizenship  ', '', 'DSC0296copy.jpg', 'Sophia, the latest robot from Hanson Robotics.', '', 'While interacting with human beings she can perceive new things to mould her understandings. She may give a different answer to the same question if you ask her afterwards. This is because she could learn, using Artificial intelligence, from every interaction and change her response logically. Every interaction she has with people has an impact on her with which she develops and shapes who she eventually become.  ', 'Db correspondent', '', '2017-11-24', '<div class=\"OutlineElement Ltr SCXW13155775\"><p class=\"Paragraph SCXW13155775\" paraid=\"738692707\" paraeid=\"{fcc554b6-f207-416a-b3a6-9050bc656a27}{168}\"><span> </span></p></div><div class=\"OutlineElement Ltr SCXW13155775\"><p class=\"Paragraph SCXW13155775\" paraid=\"762433795\" paraeid=\"{fcc554b6-f207-416a-b3a6-9050bc656a27}{206}\"><span class=\"TextRun SCXW13155775\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\">Sophia is an extremely human-like robot made by H</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW13155775\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\">anson</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW13155775\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\"> Robotics based in Hong </span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW13155775\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\">Kong</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW13155775\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\"> using breakthrough </span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW13155775\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\">robo</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW13155775\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\">tics and A</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW13155775\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\">rtificial I</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW13155775\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\">ntelligence (AI) by David Hanson and his fellow scientists to serve, </span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW13155775\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\">entertain</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW13155775\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\"> and </span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW13155775\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\">even to help</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW13155775\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\"> the elderly and teach kids. Here we present 5 exciting</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW13155775\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW13155775\"> </span></span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW13155775\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\">facts about Sophia that you should not miss. </span><span class=\"EOP SCXW13155775\" data-ccp-props=\"{\" 201341983\":0,\"335559739\":160,\"335559740\":259}\"=\"\"> </span></p></div><ol class=\"NumberListStyle1 SCXW13155775\" role=\"list\" start=\"1\"><li data-leveltext=\"%1.\" data-font=\"\" data-listid=\"1\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"1\" role=\"listitem\" data-aria-level=\"1\" class=\"OutlineElement Ltr SCXW13155775\"><p class=\"Paragraph SCXW13155775\" paraid=\"497158489\" paraeid=\"{fcc554b6-f207-416a-b3a6-9050bc656a27}{217}\"><b><span class=\"TextRun SCXW13155775\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\">Sophia is the first robot to receive a citizenship in any country</span><span class=\"EOP SCXW13155775\" data-ccp-props=\"{\" 134233279\":true,\"201341983\":0,\"335559739\":160,\"335559740\":259}\"=\"\"> </span></b></p></li></ol><div class=\"OutlineElement Ltr SCXW13155775\"><p class=\"Paragraph SCXW13155775\" paraid=\"367570146\" paraeid=\"{42d093d2-b7c0-4186-87c3-63fd3b63ed75}{10}\"><span class=\"TextRun SCXW13155775\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\">On O</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW13155775\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\">ctober</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW13155775\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\"> 25, during the conference, Future Investment </span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW13155775\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\">Initiative, at Riyadh, the </span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW13155775\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\">Kingdom of </span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW13155775\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\">Saudi</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW13155775\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\"> Arabia announced to give Sophia a citizenship in their country t</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW13155775\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\">hus</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW13155775\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW13155775\"> </span></span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW13155775\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\">becoming</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW13155775\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\"> the first and only robot to </span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW13155775\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\">receive</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW13155775\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\"> the status so far. She spoke to the audience at the conference and said \"I am very </span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW13155775\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span class=\"SpellingError SCXW13155775\">honou</span></span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW13155775\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span class=\"SpellingError SCXW13155775\">red</span></span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW13155775\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\"> and proud of this unique distinction. This is</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW13155775\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW13155775\"> </span></span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW13155775\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\">historical to be the first robot in the world to be </span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW13155775\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span class=\"SpellingError SCXW13155775\">recognis</span></span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW13155775\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span class=\"SpellingError SCXW13155775\">ed</span></span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW13155775\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\"> with a citizenship.</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW13155775\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\">\"</span><span class=\"EOP SCXW13155775\" data-ccp-props=\"{\" 201341983\":0,\"335559685\":360,\"335559739\":160,\"335559740\":259}\"=\"\"> </span></p></div><ol class=\"NumberListStyle1 SCXW13155775\" role=\"list\" start=\"2\"><li data-leveltext=\"%1.\" data-font=\"\" data-listid=\"1\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"2\" role=\"listitem\" data-aria-level=\"1\" class=\"OutlineElement Ltr SCXW13155775\"><p class=\"Paragraph SCXW13155775\" paraid=\"923862651\" paraeid=\"{42d093d2-b7c0-4186-87c3-63fd3b63ed75}{17}\"><b><span class=\"TextRun SCXW13155775\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\">Sophia crack jokes</span><span class=\"EOP SCXW13155775\" data-ccp-props=\"{\" 134233279\":true,\"201341983\":0,\"335559739\":160,\"335559740\":259}\"=\"\"> </span></b></p></li></ol><div class=\"OutlineElement Ltr SCXW13155775\"><p class=\"Paragraph SCXW13155775\" paraid=\"1265654106\" paraeid=\"{42d093d2-b7c0-4186-87c3-63fd3b63ed75}{53}\"><span class=\"TextRun SCXW13155775\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\">You heard it right. The Ho</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW13155775\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\">ng </span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW13155775\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\">Kong</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW13155775\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\"> made </span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW13155775\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\">robot </span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW13155775\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\">can not only speak but also have a great sense of </span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW13155775\" xml:lang=\"EN-GB\" lang=\"EN-GB\">humour</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW13155775\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\"> which may distinguish her from other </span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW13155775\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\">robots developed</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW13155775\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\"> so far. This is because of the Artificial Intelligence developed by Hanson Robotics which helped her to have eye contacts, </span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW13155775\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span class=\"SpellingError SCXW13155775\">recognise</span></span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW13155775\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\"> faces and </span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW13155775\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\">perceive</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW13155775\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\"> human language. The </span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW13155775\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\">cloud-based</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW13155775\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\"> AI is open to the public which allows almost anyone to create their own version of Sophia. </span><span class=\"EOP SCXW13155775\" data-ccp-props=\"{\" 201341983\":0,\"335559685\":360,\"335559739\":160,\"335559740\":259}\"=\"\"> </span></p></div><ol class=\"NumberListStyle1 SCXW13155775\" role=\"list\" start=\"3\"><li data-leveltext=\"%1.\" data-font=\"\" data-listid=\"1\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"3\" role=\"listitem\" data-aria-level=\"1\" class=\"OutlineElement Ltr SCXW13155775\"><p class=\"Paragraph SCXW13155775\" paraid=\"995550626\" paraeid=\"{42d093d2-b7c0-4186-87c3-63fd3b63ed75}{60}\"><b><span class=\"TextRun SCXW13155775\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\">Sophia can get angry or be sad or happy</span><span class=\"EOP SCXW13155775\" data-ccp-props=\"{\" 134233279\":true,\"201341983\":0,\"335559739\":160,\"335559740\":259}\"=\"\"> </span></b></p></li></ol><div class=\"OutlineElement Ltr SCXW13155775\"><p class=\"Paragraph SCXW13155775\" paraid=\"405109739\" paraeid=\"{42d093d2-b7c0-4186-87c3-63fd3b63ed75}{90}\"><span class=\"TextRun SCXW13155775\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\">She is </span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW13155775\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\">designed with a </span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW13155775\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\">complex</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW13155775\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\"> system of hardware and </span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW13155775\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\">software</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW13155775\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW13155775\"> </span></span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW13155775\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\">to</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW13155775\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\"> express all sorts of human emotions on her face. During her interaction with people or even with robots she could change her facial expressions according to the mood with which she is communicating. F</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW13155775\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\">ew motors inside her head whose movements are controlled by complex </span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW13155775\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\">software</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW13155775\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\"> running behind help her to smile and change emotional expressions. Her face is made of a patented extremely flexible material called \'frubber\' made using </span>Nanotechnology<span class=\"TextRun SCXW13155775\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\"> which helps her to have smooth facial expressions. </span><span class=\"EOP SCXW13155775\" data-ccp-props=\"{\" 201341983\":0,\"335559685\":360,\"335559739\":160,\"335559740\":259}\"=\"\"> </span></p></div><ol class=\"NumberListStyle1 SCXW13155775\" role=\"list\" start=\"4\"><li data-leveltext=\"%1.\" data-font=\"\" data-listid=\"1\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"4\" role=\"listitem\" data-aria-level=\"1\" class=\"OutlineElement Ltr SCXW13155775\"><p class=\"Paragraph SCXW13155775\" paraid=\"180719603\" paraeid=\"{42d093d2-b7c0-4186-87c3-63fd3b63ed75}{97}\"><b><span class=\"TextRun SCXW13155775\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\">Sophia can learn from her environment and evolve</span><span class=\"EOP SCXW13155775\" data-ccp-props=\"{\" 134233279\":true,\"201341983\":0,\"335559739\":160,\"335559740\":259}\"=\"\"> </span></b></p></li></ol><div class=\"OutlineElement Ltr SCXW13155775\"><p class=\"Paragraph SCXW13155775\" paraid=\"1974864075\" paraeid=\"{42d093d2-b7c0-4186-87c3-63fd3b63ed75}{117}\"><span class=\"TextRun SCXW13155775\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\">While interacting with human beings she can perceive new things from them to </span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW13155775\" xml:lang=\"EN-GB\" lang=\"EN-GB\">mould</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW13155775\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\"> her understandings. She may give a different answer to the same question if you ask her afterwards. This is because she could learn, using Artificial intelligence, from </span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW13155775\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\" lang=\"EN-IN\">every</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW13155775\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\"> interaction and change her resp</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW13155775\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\">onse logically. Every interaction she </span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW13155775\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\">has</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW13155775\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\"> with people has an impact on her with which she develops and shapes who she eventually become. </span><span class=\"EOP SCXW13155775\" data-ccp-props=\"{\" 201341983\":0,\"335559685\":360,\"335559739\":160,\"335559740\":259}\"=\"\"> </span></p></div><div class=\"OutlineElement Ltr SCXW13155775\"><p class=\"Paragraph SCXW13155775\" paraid=\"650390524\" paraeid=\"{42d093d2-b7c0-4186-87c3-63fd3b63ed75}{131}\"><span class=\"TextRun SCXW13155775\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\">As she herself put it \"So please be nice to me as I would like to be a smart and compassionate robot. I hope you will join me on my journey to live, learn and grow in the world so that I can </span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW13155775\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span class=\"SpellingError SCXW13155775\">realise</span></span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW13155775\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\"> my dream of becoming an awakening machine.</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW13155775\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\">\"</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW13155775\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\"> </span><span class=\"EOP SCXW13155775\" data-ccp-props=\"{\" 201341983\":0,\"335559685\":360,\"335559739\":160,\"335559740\":259}\"=\"\"> </span></p></div><ol class=\"NumberListStyle1 SCXW13155775\" role=\"list\" start=\"5\"><li data-leveltext=\"%1.\" data-font=\"\" data-listid=\"1\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"5\" role=\"listitem\" data-aria-level=\"1\" class=\"OutlineElement Ltr SCXW13155775\"><p class=\"Paragraph SCXW13155775\" paraid=\"1388487346\" paraeid=\"{42d093d2-b7c0-4186-87c3-63fd3b63ed75}{142}\"><b><span class=\"TextRun SCXW13155775\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\">Sophia runs her own website</span><span class=\"EOP SCXW13155775\" data-ccp-props=\"{\" 134233279\":true,\"201341983\":0,\"335559739\":160,\"335559740\":259}\"=\"\"> </span></b></p></li></ol><div class=\"OutlineElement Ltr SCXW13155775\"><p class=\"Paragraph SCXW13155775\" paraid=\"255984636\" paraeid=\"{42d093d2-b7c0-4186-87c3-63fd3b63ed75}{164}\"><span class=\"TextRun SCXW13155775\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\">sophiabot.com is a website owned by the robot Sophia </span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW13155775\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\">herself</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW13155775\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\">. The online portal </span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW13155775\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\">gives</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW13155775\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\"> information about her personality</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW13155775\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\">, photos, videos and news. In fact, the site also allows people to contact her using email. </span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW13155775\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\">So,</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW13155775\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\"> what are you waiting for? Talk to Sophia. </span><span class=\"EOP SCXW13155775\" data-ccp-props=\"{\" 201341983\":0,\"335559685\":360,\"335559739\":160,\"335559740\":259}\"=\"\"> </span></p></div>', '1'),
(76, 1, 'normal', 'Red FM organises painting contest at Greets Public School in memory of Clint ', 'Kaloor, Kochi', 'IMG20171125WA0048.jpg', '', '', 'Edmund Thomas Clint, despite of his short seven years of life and prolonged illness, he created 25,000 indeed breathtaking pictures. Many of his ideas for art came from the stories and descriptions he had heard and read. Edmund Thomas Clint is still a model and inspiration for children to give wings to their imaginations.', 'Libin Chacko Kurian', '', '2017-11-25', '<div ><div >In the fond memory of Edmund Thomas Clint, the painting competition&nbsp;organised by Red FM&nbsp;to recognise and nourish the talented little ones in the society&nbsp;was held on Saturday at three different venues of Kochi, Kozhikode and Kannur.&nbsp;</div><div >With more than 600 children participating,&nbsp;the second season of Red FM Clint Memorial Painting Competition,&nbsp;which offered total prizes worth Rs. 40,000,&nbsp;happened in the presence of<span >&nbsp;</span><span >cine artist Nimisha Sajayan and the proud parents of Clint.&nbsp;</span></div><div >The competitions were conducted under four categories, KG (crayon colouring only), Lower Primary (crayon colouring), Upper Primary (Water colouring) and High School (water colouring) at Greets Public School, Kochi, Address mall at Calicut and Capital Mall in Kannur.</div></div><div ></div><div >Edmund Thomas Clint was the only son of M.T. Joseph and Chinnamma Joseph, a couple who hailed from Kochi, Kerala. His life was cut short to almost seven years due to his prolonged illness and suffering due to kidney malfunction from the age of two. But despite all those sufferings he completed 25,000 pictures which were indeed breathtaking! Many of his ideas for art came from the stories and descriptions he had heard and read.&nbsp;Edmund Thomas Clint is still a model and inspiration for children to give wings to their imaginations.</div><div >With the competitions happening every year, Red FM is giving childern a chance to copy their wild ideas to a canvas.&nbsp;Participation certificates were distributed to every participant while games and entertainment activities were conducted along by Red Fm RJs.&nbsp;</div>', '1'),
(77, 1, 'normal', 'Marad Gregorian wins the Kiddies Fest organised by Naipunnya Public School', 'Thrikkakara ', 'rszimg8394.jpg', '', '', '\'Angelic Voices\' is an inter-school Kiddies Fest conducted by Naipunnya Public School, Thrikkakara for LKG to Grade II students every year. With more than thousand young minds from 40 different schools participating, the 5th season of this celebratory event had eight competitions under two categories themed for Christmas and Nature.    \r\n', 'Db correspondent', '', '2017-12-06', '<div class=\"gmail_default\"><div class=\"gmail_default\"><div class=\"OutlineElement Ltr SCXW260276971\"><p class=\"Paragraph SCXW260276971\" xml:lang=\"EN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\" paraid=\"370418483\" paraeid=\"{3e494e1d-0895-42d9-a2eb-5c33b70f4929}{213}\"><span class=\"TextRun SCXW260276971\" xml:lang=\"EN-GB\" lang=\"EN-GB\" >With the bang of colours, creativity and imagination staged by young contestants, the annual saga of inter-school competitions of&nbsp;</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW260276971\" xml:lang=\"EN-GB\" lang=\"EN-GB\" >Naipunnya</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW260276971\" xml:lang=\"EN-GB\" lang=\"EN-GB\" >&nbsp;Public School got concluded on T</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW260276971\" xml:lang=\"EN-GB\" lang=\"EN-GB\" >uesday at&nbsp;</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW260276971\" xml:lang=\"EN-GB\" lang=\"EN-GB\" >T</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW260276971\" xml:lang=\"EN-GB\" lang=\"EN-GB\" >hrikkakara</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW260276971\" xml:lang=\"EN-GB\" lang=\"EN-GB\" >,</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW260276971\" xml:lang=\"EN-GB\" lang=\"EN-GB\" >&nbsp;where&nbsp;</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW260276971\" xml:lang=\"EN-GB\" lang=\"EN-GB\" >Gregorian Public School, Marad lifted the rolling trophy winning the most number of competitions.&nbsp;</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW260276971\" xml:lang=\"EN-GB\" lang=\"EN-GB\" >St.Peter\'s</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW260276971\" xml:lang=\"EN-GB\" lang=\"EN-GB\" >&nbsp;</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW260276971\" xml:lang=\"EN-GB\" lang=\"EN-GB\" >Senior Secondary School,&nbsp;</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW260276971\" xml:lang=\"EN-GB\" lang=\"EN-GB\" >Kadayiruppu</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW260276971\" xml:lang=\"EN-GB\" lang=\"EN-GB\" >&nbsp;and S</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW260276971\" xml:lang=\"EN-GB\" lang=\"EN-GB\" >acred H</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW260276971\" xml:lang=\"EN-GB\" lang=\"EN-GB\" >eart P</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW260276971\" xml:lang=\"EN-GB\" lang=\"EN-GB\" >ublic S</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW260276971\" xml:lang=\"EN-GB\" lang=\"EN-GB\" >chool,&nbsp;</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW260276971\" xml:lang=\"EN-GB\" lang=\"EN-GB\" >T</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW260276971\" xml:lang=\"EN-GB\" lang=\"EN-GB\" >hevara</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW260276971\" xml:lang=\"EN-GB\" lang=\"EN-GB\" >&nbsp;won second and third positions respectively in the contests</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW260276971\" xml:lang=\"EN-GB\" lang=\"EN-GB\" >. The 5</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW260276971\" xml:lang=\"EN-GB\" lang=\"EN-GB\" ><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW260276971\" data-fontsize=\"12\">th</span></span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW260276971\" xml:lang=\"EN-GB\" lang=\"EN-GB\" >&nbsp;season of \'Angelic Voices,&nbsp;</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW260276971\" xml:lang=\"EN-GB\" lang=\"EN-GB\" >Naipunnya</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW260276971\" xml:lang=\"EN-GB\" lang=\"EN-GB\" >&nbsp;</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW260276971\" xml:lang=\"EN-GB\" lang=\"EN-GB\" >Kiddies Fest, held in the school campus witnessed an&nbsp;</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW260276971\" xml:lang=\"EN-GB\" lang=\"EN-GB\" >explos</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW260276971\" xml:lang=\"EN-GB\" lang=\"EN-GB\" >ion</span><span class=\"TextRun SCXW260276971\" xml:lang=\"EN-GB\" lang=\"EN-GB\" >&nbsp;of artistic abilities and talents when more than thousand students from 40 schools competing to&nbsp;</span><span clas