(30, 'upcoming', 'Greater Kochi Greenathon', '2018-04-15 06:00:00', '2018-04-15 08:00:00', 'Valummel, Kochi', '<p style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; margin-bottom: 1em; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.1px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif;\">Greater Kochi Greenathon</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.1px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif;\">An initiative to promote \'Clean and Green\' Greater Kochi along with to support underprivileged kids.<br>Registration at: Goeventz.com</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.1px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif;\">Event Details:<br>Event: Greater Kochi Greenathon<br>When: 15th April 2018<br>Where: Kochi, Kerala.</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.1px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif;\">Category:<br>1 Km Kids FUN Run (Age 8+)<br>3 Km Senior Citizen / Fun Run (Age 40+)<br>5 Km Green Run (Age 10 +)<br>10 Km Fitness Run (Age 18+)</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.1px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif;\">Entry Fee: Rs. 500/-&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.1px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif;\">1 Km and 3 Km registration money will be contributed to Let’s Go Green Together initiative and to support under privilege kids.</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136); f