Roboto, sans-serif; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.1px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif;\">- Music and lot of Fun</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.1px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif;\">Discount options:</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.1px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif;\">-Group discount above 25 no.</span><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\"><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>', '1', 'Untitled.png'),
(31, 'upcoming', 'Kerala is #trending. #FUTURE', '2018-03-22 09:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'Hotel Le Meridien, Kochi', '<p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; font-family: &quot;Raleway Webfont&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; line-height: 35px; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased !important;\">#FUTURE would be the most high profile Digital Event and the best ever of its kind conducted in the state of Kerala. The two day event will see the convergence of achievers, professionals, entrepreneurs, academicians, key influencers and other stakeholders in the knowledge industry from across the globe. They will discuss though value adding sessions – key notes and panel discussions - emerging trends, ground realities and opportunities that would help individuals, enterprises and entrepreneurs to compete and lead in a digital world.</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-family: &quot;Raleway Webfont&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; line-height: 35px; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased !important;\">The theme of the event is&nbsp;<span class=\"heightlight\" style=\"color: rgb(35, 31, 32);\">‘Towards a Digital Future’</span>.</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-family: &quot;Raleway Webfont&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; line-height: 35px; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased !important;\">The purpose of #FUTURE is to inspire and energise people towards a knowledge-driven digital future. Such renewed energy, drive and aspiration should help facilitate the accelerated growth of the IT/ digital opportunities.</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-family: &quot;Raleway Webfont&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; line-height: 35px; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased !important;\">#FUTURE will be held on 2 days</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-family: &quot;Raleway Webfont&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; line-height: 35px; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased !important;\">Day 1: Thursday, 22nd March&nbsp; &nbsp;Day 2: Friday, 23rd March</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-family: &quot;Raleway Webfont&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; line-height: 35px; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased !important;\">Main Speakers at the Event:</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-family: &quot;Raleway Webfont&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; line-height: 35px; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased !important;\">Nandan Nilekani, Infosys</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-family: &quot;Raleway Webfont&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; line-height: 35px; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased !important;\">Raghuram Rajan, Former RBI Governor</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-family: &quot;Raleway Webfont&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; line-height: 35px; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased !important;\">Byju Raveendran, BYJU\'S</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-family: &quot;Raleway Webfont&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; line-height: 35px; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased !important;\">Gita Gopinath, Harvard University</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-family: &quot;Raleway Webfont&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; line-height: 35px; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased !important;\">R. Chandrashekhar, NASSCOM</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-family: &quot;Raleway Webfont&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; line-height: 35px; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased !important;\">For more details,&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-family: &quot;Raleway Webfont&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; line-height: 35px; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased !important;\">Visit the website:&nbsp;http://towardsfuture.in/</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-family: &quot;Raleway Webfont&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; line-height: 35px; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased !important;\"><br></p>', '1', 'logo2.png'),
(32, 'upcoming', 'Dance Summer Camp ', '2018-04-01 09:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'Palarivattom, Kochi', '<p>Mamangam Dance Summer Camp</p><p>Mamangam Dance School is organising ten days dance workshop for kids who have the passion to dance. The camp will concentrate on introducing contemporary dance and Kalari along with non-fire cooking, percussion, fun science, movie, crafts workshop, archery and fun.</p><p>It will be a complete entertainment for kids packed with fun. Learning becomes simple added with an element of fun to it and with this programme kids can also choose the art they love.&nbsp;</p>', '1', 'mamangam-home-image.jpg'),
(33, 'upcoming', 'Vacation Summer Class!', '2018-04-16 09:00:00', '2018-04-30 03:00:00', 'Ravipuram, Kochi', '<p>Summer Vacation&nbsp;Class</p><p>Venue: Designer Institute of Interior Design, Ravipuram</p><p>Age Groups: 5 to 15 years</p><p>Course Fee: 5000/-</p><p>Time schedule: 10:30 a.m to 3:00 p.m</p><p>Want to develop the qualities of your kid? This vacation class offers learning and fun. Children can learn technology through computer graphics also. Classes on personality development, visual arts, clay modelling, science quizzes are also arranged.</p><p>For more details:</p><p>Contact: 0484-400081</p><p><br></p>', '1', '32508summervacationclasses.jpg'),
(34, 'upcoming', 'Storytelling Workshop- In association with Cochin Theatre Collective  ', '2018-04-27 11:00:00', '2018-04-28 04:00:00', 'Lotus Club, Kochi', '<p>Storytelling Workshop- A Baanyan Tree Initiative, In Association with Cochin English Theatre Collective</p><p>Baanyan Tree specialises in the Growth strategy to make effective leaders for the corporate world. Through such an initiative they are focusing on providing a platform for the young leaders amongst you.</p><p>The topics covered would include language skills, communication skills, engaging audience, body language, good storytelling qualities and so on. It will altogether improve the performance skills of your kid! It will motivate children to include their creativity in the stories too.</p><p>Age Group: 8-18 years</p><p>Registration Fee: 1500/-</p><p>For registration and more details:</p><p>Log on to, http://www.baanyantree.org/</p><p style=\"text-align: center; \"><br></p>', '1', 'EventCover-02.png'),
(35, 'upcoming', 'Monsoon plunge 2', '2018-07-07 10:00:00', '2018-07-08 19:00:00', 'Thattekkad, Ernakulam', '<p>Weather is a great metaphor for life and so is Monsoon for Happiness!!!<br style=\"\">This time lets go for a camp has focused a frame of a great monsoon with pouring rains, lush green forests, tumbling and blushing waterfalls, and most importantly the drenched smiley faces!<br style=\"\">Let\'s bring back the nostalgic moments we had gone through our monsoon days. Together let\'s get wet in rain, climb the hills, dip in pools as the rain falls on us, let\'s grin like a child and dance with it!&nbsp;<br></p>', '1', '32703950_832185920325604_7960794919054868480_n.jpg'),
(36, 'upcoming', 'Rise Up', '2018-07-22 19:30:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'BHASKAREEYAM CONVENTION CENTRE, MAMANGALAM, ELAMAKKARA, KALOOR, ERNAKULAM', '<p><span style=\"font-weight: 700; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 13px;\">Rise Up</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 13px;\">&nbsp;is not a motivational training or workshop; it is a Visual, Auditory and Kinesthetic experience which cannot be explained in words. Techniques and methodologies are developed using extensive research on Thought Process Re-engineering by&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-weight: 700; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 13px;\">Mr Sajeev Nair.</span><br></p>', '1', 'Riseup.jpeg'),
(37, 'upcoming', 'Art Workshop by TAOS', '2018-07-28 10:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'ABAD Nucleus Mall Kochi, Poonithura, Maradu, Kochi, Kerala', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">An art workshop by TAOS in collaboration&nbsp;with Kashi art gallery</span><br></p>', '1', 'artworkshop.jpg'),
(38, 'upcoming', 'Kochi Hub Meet 2018', '2018-07-20 15:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', ' Toc H Institute of Science and Technology, Arakkunnam P.O, Kochi, India 682313, Kochi, India', '<p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(68, 68, 68);\">With the recurring success stories of KHM, IEEE KOCHI HUB is back with its pre-eminent event of the year - KOCHI HUB MEET 2018!</p><p style=\"margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 12px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(68, 68, 68);\">With a whole range of stimulating pursuits like techno-managerial workshops, sessions &amp; other fun delights, KHM provides a podium to celebrate self-build up!</p>', '1', 'hubneet.jpg'),
(39, 'upcoming', 'NITC Model United Nations', '2018-08-04 10:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'THE CENTER HOTEL, MIG HOUSING SOCIETY, PANAMPILLY NAGAR, ERNAKULAM, INDIA', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(29, 33, 41); font-size: 13px;\">At NITCMUN, take a step closer to becoming an active and globally aware citizen in this progressive era of globalization. Seek a peaceful, prosperous and free world, a world of good neighbours, living on terms of equality and mutual respect. Join hands to mobilise a delegation of young minds with a zeal to make the world a better place. For making peace in a world of war, isn\'t a one-man job.</span><br></p>', '1', 'NITC.png'),
(40, 'upcoming', 'Kochi Culinary Fest', '2018-09-02 10:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'Rotary Hall, Panampilly Nagar, Kochi', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">A platform to share and taste. An event focusing mainly school and college students. However, there is also a general category available. It is a golden opportunity for them to prove their efficiency in cooking. A program dedicated to all those who love cooking as well as eating.</span><br></p>', '1', 'culinaryfest.jpg'),
(41, 'upcoming', 'Cochin International Boat show', '2018-09-26 10:00:00', '2018-09-28 18:00:00', 'Bolgatty Palace and Island Resort', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(111, 114, 135); font-family: &quot;Neue Plak&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">CIBS 2018 will be the most prestigious Maritime &amp; Boat Event in India. The geographical location of Cochin, makes it the most suitable and convenient venue to host an event of this nature. The show will attract buyers from the leisure marine, tourism, fishing and other related industries.</span><br></p>', '1', 'Cochin-International-Boat-Show-COPY-1900x700_c.jpg'),
(42, 'upcoming', 'International Conference on Nanomedicine and Tissue Engineering (ICNT)', '2018-10-12 09:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'Ettumanoor', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">The conference will feature keynote addresses, a number of plenary sessions, invited talks and contributed lectures focusing on specific tenets of Nanomedicine and tissue engineering.</span><br></p>', '1', 'ICNT.jpg'),
(43, 'upcoming', 'Ernakulam Public Library Film Club Movie Screening', '2018-10-21 10:00:00', '2018-10-21 12:00:00', 'Cochin, Kerala', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(61, 61, 61); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 11px;\">This event repeats weekly until 12 Jul 2019.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(61, 61, 61); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 11px;\">Event details may change at any time, always check with the event organizer when planning to attend this event or purchase tickets.</span><br></p>', '1', 'ernakulam-public-library-film-club-mov-61.png'),
(44, 'upcoming', 'Art Show', '2018-11-01 11:00:00', '2018-11-01 18:00:00', 'Indriyam Art Gallery, Jew Town, Kappalandimukku, Mattancherry, Kochi, Kerala 682002', '<p>\'Bounded within and bounded beyond\', curated by Mithul MT, showcasing works by Anuraj, Reshma and Vinil opens. For more details contact: 9633126736</p>', '1', 'artgallery.jpeg'),
(45, 'upcoming', 'Book Fair', '2018-11-01 10:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'Ernakulathappan ground, Shiva Temple, Durbar Hall Rd, Marine Drive, Ernakulam, Kerala 682011', '<p>The Kochi International Book Fair (KIBF) organised by Antharashtra Pusthakotsava Samithy opens. Discussions and seminars will be held as part of it.&nbsp;</p>', '1', 'bookfest.jpg'),
(46, 'upcoming', 'Prathidhwani:Srishti 2018 - Pencil Drawing, Painting and Cartoon', '2018-11-10 09:00:00', '2018-11-10 18:00:00', 'Infopark  Kochi, 682042', '<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(111, 114, 135); font-family: &quot;Neue Plak&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">\'<span style=\"font-weight: 700; padding-top: 0px;\">Prathidhwani Srishti</span>\' is the sole event that targets to bring out strong, hidden creative talents of techies. We cordially invite eminent and aspiring writers to rush their entries to Prathidhwani Srishti 2018. Contests will be in&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Short Story, Poem, Creative Writing - (Malayalam, English), Cartoon, Pencil Drawing and Painting.</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 10px 0px 0px; color: rgb(111, 114, 135); font-family: &quot;Neue Plak&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">Last Date of submission of entries is&nbsp;<span style=\"padding-top: 0px;\">November 8th 2018.</span></p>', '1', 'Srishti2018.jpg');
